Bali throwback! Why? Because i can. Lol. Anyway i'm Still in Dolomites but it seems the fog keeps following me üò≠ i wanted to see the mountains! Haha. But anyway, the vibe here is very very surreal and peaceful. Thank you, fog.

It is an unYUZUal moment when you bring your favorite drink to another continent ‚ú® // Suka banget sama @yuzuindonesia , minuman teh dengan sensasi yg beda bikin aku tambah fresh buat jalan-jalan dan foto di Paris //
. .

Bagi kamu yang ingin cobain, bisa dapatkan langsung YUZU di Alfamart (Jabodetabek) dan buruan juga ikutan #UnYUZUalChallenge di www.yuzu.co.id dan menangin iPhone 7! #LiveUnYUZUal // taken by @capra311

Finally, Dolomites! Long time ago I saw a picture from this area, from one and only, @brahmino . He took it beautifully and i promised myself that one day I have to visit this place. I put it in my bucket list. Years after that, i am here now. Feel so peaceful in the land of majestic mountains and landscapes. When @capra311 drove me here yesterday, I couldn't stop saying, "oh my gosh!!" on every corner that we passed. Though the weather is not so kind, but i still feel grateful to witness this kind of beauty. So here is the first picture of Dolomites from Lago Antorno ‚ú®

What's your favorite place in Paris? // Sila cek @ezytravel kalau mau jalan jalan seru di Eropa ya! Banyak paket tour ke eropa dan Paris salah satu destinasinya :) #ezytraveleurope #ezytravelpuanindya

The oldest spiral staircase that i've ever shoot. It was a very nice surprise from @capra311 when we walked around the city. A spontaneous act from him that i like. Suddenly he changed the route and took me here. He said, "this one is a very beautiful staircase but we can't go in because it's private building" then suddenly he opened the door and let me walked up the stairs by myself. The atmosphere was quite dark and gloomy, something that i liked. And when i looked down, geez, i'm in love..

#shegotwiiings happy kartini's day! // at the end of the day, we cherished ourselves with sunset and a bundle of energy from @redbullindo . The conversation was nice there. A little gossip and a big proud for being woman who loves travel and dare to meet a lot of new people and learn new things from them. Oh, the joy of traveling!

Along the way, there was a ceremony in this temple. Balinese women walked in the sunshine with their traditional dresses. It was such a beautiful surprise for me because i've never seen the ceremony before with place as beautiful as this one. This is what i like about traveling. The surprising moments that gives you goosebumps! #shegotwiiings @redbullindo

#shegotwiiings !! A throwback from one of my happiest days with my girl friends. The road trip vibes with your best ones. The itchy feet because you can't wait for the salty breeze... try to forget our problems with work for a while and have girl conversation about what to wear in the next destinations lol. I thankful to have more emotions and strength. To be sane while you have your monthly problems haha. Let's celebrate for being a woman! üí™üèΩ @redbullindo

@capra311 celebrating his birthday with this moody view from @fsparis . We couldn't ask for more. Best bed, best dinner in @legeorgeparis , best service, best location, with the best view ever üñ§ #georgeV #fsparis #fourseasons @fourseasons
